OL,3,CHundreds set to lose their jobs at
OL,4,CBarry chemical factory
OL,6,FHundreds of people will lose their
OL,7,Fjobs at a chemical factory in Barry,
OL,8,FVale of Glamorgan.
OL,10,FDow, who run the site, has confirmed
OL,11,F220 people will be let go after
OL,12,Fannouncing the potential for job cuts
OL,13,Fearlier this year.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Dow said it "will shut
OL,16,Fdown the basic siloxanes operations at
OL,17,Fits Barry, U.K. site...."
