OL,6,FIt continued: "As part of the
OL,7,Fconsultation process with employees
OL,8,Fand union representatives, Dow has
OL,9,Ftaken steps to reduce the number of
OL,10,Froles affected from 291 to
OL,11,Fapproximately 220, to be phased out
OL,12,Fover the next three to four years."
OL,14,FJob cuts are expected to begin in mid-
OL,15,F2026.
