OL,6,FThe company acknowledged it is
OL,7,F"difficult news for its employees and
OL,8,Fthe local community". It added: "This
OL,9,Fdecision is in no way a reflection on
OL,10,Fthe Barry team, who have shown
OL,11,Ftremendous professionalism and
OL,12,Fdedication.
OL,14,F"The Barry site remains a vital part
OL,15,Fof Dow's operations. While basic
OL,16,Fsiloxanes production will cease,
OL,17,Fspecialty silicones manufacturing will
OL,18,Fcontinue, supporting key industries
OL,19,Fsuch as automotive, electronics,
OL,20,Fenergy, construction, and personal
OL,21,Fcare."
