OL,3,CHundreds set to lose their jobs at
OL,4,CBarry chemical factory
OL,6,FThe company, which produces a wide
OL,7,Frange of silicon products, has wholly
OL,8,Fowned the Barry site since 2016 and
OL,9,Fnow employs 850 people on a 160-acre
OL,10,Fsite.
OL,12,FDow has manufacturing sites in 30
OL,13,Fcountries, employs around 36,000
OL,14,Fpeople globally and was among the
OL,15,Fthree largest chemical producers in
OL,16,Fthe world in 2021. However, it says
OL,17,Fcheap competition from abroad is
OL,18,Fbehind the cuts.
