OL,6,FIts board has also approved cuts at
OL,7,Ftwo of its other European sites, both
OL,8,Fin Germany.
OL,10,FJim Fitterling, Dow chair and CEO
OL,11,Fsaid: "Our industry in Europe
OL,12,Fcontinues to face difficult market
OL,13,Fdynamics, as well as an ongoing
OL,14,Fchallenging cost and demand landscape.
OL,16,F"Over the past decade, we have
OL,17,Fdemonstrated Dow's commitment to
OL,18,Foperating with a best-owner mindset by
OL,19,Ftaking proactive actions across higher-
OL,20,Fcost or non-strategic assets.
