OL,6,F"Looking ahead, we remain committed to
OL,7,Frealising the value of our incremental
OL,8,Fgrowth investments and enhancing
OL,9,Fprofitability and cash flow through
OL,10,Fmore than $6 billion in near-term cash
OL,11,Fsupport."
OL,13,FThe union Unite described the move as
OL,14,F"devastating" but said negotiations it
OL,15,Fhad had with Dow meant fewer jobs
OL,16,Flosses.
OL,18,FInitially almost 300 jobs were at risk
OL,19,Fbut now that number is 220 - with
OL,20,Falmost 150 of these voluntary
OL,21,Fredundancies.
