OL,6,FUnite Regional officer Anthony Simpson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Unite's hard work in
OL,8,Fnegotiations has managed to save some
OL,9,Fof the jobs at risk and ensure that
OL,10,Fthose who are being made redundant
OL,11,Freceive enhanced packages.
OL,13,F"However, going forward we need to
OL,14,Fensure there is government support for
OL,15,Fretraining across the board. We need a
OL,16,Fproactive industrial strategy that
OL,17,Funderpins our manufacturing industry
OL,18,Fto ensure there is decent future
OL,19,Femployment in the Barry area."
